&lt;li&gt;Highly organized, impeccable attention to detail, and great at prioritizing what needs to get done now, and what should wait until later&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Love ideating, executing, and testing new ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are action-oriented; you understand that ideas are easy, but implementation is where the magic is&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work well in a fast-paced, dynamic environment and are able to manage competing priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
