&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with sales/acquisition and operations teams to onboard new provider practices by prioritizing and managing complex processes across multiple accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driving practice performance by effectively communicating feature value and handling objections to maintain setup and increase buy-in&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being incredibly detailed oriented, able to manage multiple projects simultaneously

